headline: Targa Resources: The Price Is Not Always Right (Rating Downgrade)
summary: Targa Resources has outperformed my 2026 price target with strong growth. Learn why TRGP stock is downgraded to a hold despite new projects and growth plans.

headline: Q3 2024: Another Strong Quarter For Midstream/MLP Payouts
summary: Dividend growth has been a key tailwind for midstream in recent years, enhancing already generous payouts. Those tailwinds continued in Q3 2024 and are expected to extend to 2025 and beyond.
